## 2. The Debt Avalanche Strategy

This is the mathematically optimal way to eliminate debt:

**Steps:**
1. List all debts by interest rate (highest to lowest)
2. Pay minimum on everything
3. Put any extra money toward the highest-interest debt
4. When that's paid off, attack the next highest-interest debt
5. Repeat

**Why this works:**
