## 3. The Debt Snowball Strategy (Psychological)

This is not mathematically optimal, but it works psychologically:

**Steps:**
1. List debts by balance (smallest to largest)
2. Pay minimum on everything
3. Put all extra money toward the smallest debt
4. When that's paid off, apply that payment to the next smallest debt
